name: Broke
description:
When the cryptocurrencies were crashing, anxiety and bad toughts was all over me, watching my NFT's sales dropped day by day, Tezos was down to its limit, etc. During that time, I was really unproductive. So one day, I realized, why didn't I respond that situation and pour it into my work? 

Marker on A4 Paper. Scanned to JPEG.
2480 x 3508 pixels.
